---
title: Black Bean Burger Crunchy Wraps with Creamy Guac & Pico de Gallo
description: That dream you had where a veggie burger married a quesadilla and they had a baby? Well, turns out, our chefs had the same dream and here’s the result: the crunchy wrap (aka burgerdilla)! It’s a homemade Mexican-spiced black bean burger wrapped in a flour tortilla with rich queso, fresh pico, and tortilla chips for crunch. This genius concoction is pan-fried till extra-crisp. The dream ends like all the best ones do: with dollops of creamy guac and squeezes of fresh lime.
